-- Portugal, Czech Republic Tied 0-0 at Half-Time at Euro 2012
-- B y   A l e x   D u f f
-- 2012-06-21T19:35:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-21/portugal-czech-republic-tied-0-0-at-half-time-at-euro-2012.html
Portugal  and the Czech Republic were
tied 0-0 at half-time of the first European Championship soccer
quarterfinal.  Cristiano Ronaldo hit the post for Portugal in stoppage
time at the end of the first half in Warsaw.  The winner advances to face defending champion Spain or
France in the semifinals.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alex Duff at 
 aduff4@bloomberg.net  